  "title": "Production Operator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Load and unloading of parts.</li><li>Assisting in production.</li><li>Any other tasks as assigned by Supervisor.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Nitec in any discipline or equivalent.</li><li>Process 1 years of relevant work experience in assembly line is preferred.</li><li>Those without experience are welcome to apply as training will be provided.</li></ul><p>Working hours: 7.30am to 4.30pm (Mon to Fri)</p><p>Overtime claimable</p><p></p><p>Interested applicants are welcome to send your resume to career@oneconsulting-global.com</p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel: R1107675</p><p>Agency no. 07C3676</p>",
